        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "This... *Holds out her Scepter* This is the High Scepter of Celedring. The finest Elven craftsman of any age. It was taken from Middle Earth when he left it forever more. Thus it could not fall into the wrong hands. My heart gladdens to see that there are still those who fight for our cause."
